Package drivers

Class Item

java.lang.Object
drivers.Item
public class Item extends Object
Primary Item class for generating Item objects within the inventory management system. The Item class represents an item with various attributes such as SKU, item name, category, brand, item size, unit, color, type, and description. It provides getters and setters for each attribute along with JavaFX properties for seamless integration with JavaFX applications.
Author:
Arianne Acosta, Joy Arellano, Clark Rodriguez

      public Item(String SKU, String item, String category, String brand, int itemsize, String unit, String color, String type, String description)
      Constructs a new Item with the specified values for each attribute.
      Parameters:
      SKU - the Stock Keeping Unit (SKU) of the item
      item - the name of the item
      category - the category to which the item belongs
      brand - the brand of the item
      itemsize - the size of the item
      unit - the unit in which the item is measured
      color - the color of the item
      type - the type or classification of the item
      description - a description or additional information about the item
